CommerceBancorp said it will redeem effective Oct. 25, all 157,800 shares of its $2 cumulative convertible preferred stock currently outstanding at a price of $26.80 a share plus accrued dividends. 

The stock is convertible into about 414,000 common shares of CommerceBancorp stock.
The bank holding company currently has about 1.5 million common shares outstanding. 

CommerceBancorp stock rose 50 cents to $18 in national over-the-counter trading. 

